### **Feature Coverage**
- ✅ User authentication (Firebase)
- ✅ Family account management
- ✅ Character creation/editing with AI avatars
- ✅ Story generation (streaming progress)
- ✅ Memory logging (user interaction feedback)
- ✅ Prompt management & playground
- ✅ Real-time progress tracking via SSE
- ✅ Multi-AI provider support (Gemini, Groq, OpenAI)